Dear Carer Test1,
Mr Az Pro 1 has invited you to use Patients Know Best together.

Message from Az Pro 1

Please consider being my carer

To accept the invitation, please register with Patients Know Best using this link:

http://pkb-frontend-10/patientPersonalInfoForm.action?uid=2149&temp=$esc.url($tempPassword)

Questions?

  1. Is this medically secure? Patients Know Best is HIPAA-compliant for US patients and Data Protection Act compliant for European ones. The site is part of the UK NHS secure network (N3), so it is already built to NHS security standards and approved for usage with any NHS computer.
  2. Do I have to register with the web site? Yes, but registration is free and fast. Please click here: http://pkb-frontend-10/patientPersonalInfoForm.action?uid=2149&temp=$esc.url($tempPassword)
  3. What happens after I register? You can access the records of Mr Az Pro 1 to use Patients Know Best together securely.

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Log into your record to see your medical information and manage your care.

Yours,
